d-puzzles', '78M', 'Free', 'Fanatee, Inc.', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.fanatee.cody', NULL, '2', 4.00, '', 1, 1, 0, 22, 7, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2019-11-06 13:11:01', '2019-11-06 13:11:01'),
