earch, like Nielsen’s TV Ratings. Please see http://www.nielsen.com/digitalprivacy for more information.<br><br>*Restrictions apply. Access to certain content requires current subscription with participating TV provider', '9532285.png', 'freeform-stream-full-episodes-movies-live-tv', NULL, 'Free', 'Freeform', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.disney.datg.videoplatforms.android.abcf', NULL, '2', 4.00, '', 1, 1, 0, 25, 7, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2019-11-14 17:35:49', '2019-11-14 17:35:49'),
