Technical Support? Contact us: indiesupport@generagames.com', '9274369.png', 'ninja-dash-run-epic-arcade-offline-games-2020', '64M', 'Free', 'Genera Games', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.generagames.ninjadash.samuraironin.jumprpg', NULL, '2', 4.00, '', 1, 1, 0, 22, 7, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2019-11-20 18:01:20', '2019-11-20 18:01:20'),
