(457, 'Great Breakout - Funny Word Game', 'Our stickman is back with the new cross puzzle!', NULL, '<br>Word Story: Great Breakout is the sequel of Word Story, which is the world\'s best popular word games in 2018. In this game, the developer redesigns the storyline, bring Better and smarter game modes, Easy to use interface, and challenging puzzle levels. Experience the story and enlarge your vocabulary and show off your spelling skills as you pass the highest level and ranked on top of world players in this beloved word game.<br><br>The poor guy, Jack, curiously received an unknown package.  Cops arrested him after he opened the package, which is full of drugs. No matter what he explains, the judge put him into prison. Obviously, he is innocent. But who set up these things? and why?<br><br>Can Jack survive in hostile environments? Will he make friend with other prisoners? What will happen between Jack and Ada, our beautiful nurse? What makes him decide to breakout? Will him success? Will he find the truth and revenge?<br><br>Thousands of challenging word puzzles you will face in different stories. Don’t miss the most interesting word game.<br><br><b>New funny Stories</b><br>► The whole story is redesigned to be more reasonable and funny. Stickman\'s new story, including how is he arrested, his life in prison, his relationship between the beautiful nurse, how to break out, and final to find the truth and revenge. <br><br><br><b>Better and smarter game modes</b><br>► This is a great sequel game that starts out pretty easy but gets progressively more difficult as you reach the higher levels.  It is easy to play, but difficult to master! Early levels lead you in gently. When there are only a few words to spell, it’s not much trouble to complete the puzzle before. But when you’re staring at a dozen blank words, figuring out how they all join up is an invigorating test. There are literally thousands of levels to play so you\'re never going to run out of puzzles.<br><br><br><b>Daily Challenge</b><br>► Even better: every day, you receive a new puzzle, giving the game reason to stick around on your device for the long term. The challenge is always hard to solve, it makes your brain running. Once you complete the challenge, the big reward is waiting for you.<br><br><br><b>Ranks and League</b><br>► The Player League is unlocked after completing Level 20. This feature provides various rewards to the player, such as thousands of coins, and medal of honor. To get the rewards, players have to reach certain ranks, which are the sum of the stars of you have this week. <br><br><br>Features:<br>✔ Spell the right word to pass levels<br>✔ Thousands of word puzzles are waiting for you<br>✔ Everyone will have fun in the game<br>✔ No boring rules, you can enjoy stories relaxed<br>✔ Training your brain in free time<br>✔ More stories will be updated soon<br>✔ You can play offline<br><br><b>Which story would you start first? DOWNLOAD NOW!</b><br><br>If you have any question or suggestion, please contact us by great_breakout@boooea.com. Your thoughts will be important for our game.', '8285405.png', 'great-breakout-funny-word-game', '81M', 'Free', 'Great Puzzle Games', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.game.puzzle.escape.saving.noah', NULL, '2', 4.00, '', 1, 1, 0, 22, 7, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2019-11-23 20:03:34', '2019-11-23 20:03:34'),
