gher.<br>Press the ball in the bottom of the screen to select a special ball. Press again to change the ball type.<br><br>Game supports all Android screen sizes (phones and tablets) .', '9223229.png', 'magnetic-balls-bubble-shoot', '31M', 'Free', '100500games.org', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.fornetjob.springballs', NULL, '2', 4.00, '', 1, 1, 0, 22, 7, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2019-11-25 07:51:02', '2019-11-25 07:51:02'),
