le Shooter ™ are owned by Ilyon Dynamics Ltd.', '5095872.png', 'bubble-shooter', NULL, 'Free', 'Bubble Shooter', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=bubbleshooter.orig', NULL, '2', 4.00, '', 1, 1, 0, 22, 7, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2019-11-26 09:44:45', '2019-11-26 09:44:45'),
