(928, 'Bike Racer', 'Bike racer brings you the world of races and be the extreme motorbike rider. Swerve through the obstacles to reach he finish line in the shortest time possible to be on the top. Explore the desert theme with realistic movements and 3D effects. Take it to the top gear to reach the maximum speed without falling off your bikes.', NULL, 'Ride your Bikes through curvy paths on amazing desert roads, mountain off road , and city roads but be careful on dangerous turns in bike racer.  Experience the excitement and thrill of driving a dirt motorbike through a massive stadium, filled with bumps and jumps. Prove that you are the best moto auto champio and climb to the top of the leaderboards. <br><br>With the challenging racetrack experience and breathtaking graphics, you won’t be able to put your phone down. Now get ready for adrenaline fuelled racetrack action and ride your way to victory in the fastest lane of all! Can you be the best and complete all the missions in this daredevils course on your motorcycle racer? Then take a ride with this Biking Races now!<br><br>Bike Racer Game Features :<br><br>- Free to Play!<br>- Tons of Amazing Racing vehicles<br>- Amazing 3D Environments with desert themes<br>- Fast racing tracks with tricky obstacles<br>- Challenge your Facebook friends<br>- Simple and intuitive driving controls', '3467072.png', 'bike-racer', NULL, 'Free', 'Million games', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.milliongames.bikeracer2018', NULL, '2', 4.00, '', 1, 1, 0, 22, 7, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2019-11-26 11:10:37', '2019-11-26 11:10:37'),
(929, 'Rally Racer EVO®', 'Rally Racer EVO is one of the best and free rally racing games with arcade racing dynamics. If you like  arcade time attack racing games you will love it.', NULL, 'THE EVOLUTION<br> Rally Racer EVO® takes the extremism and competition of rally racing to the next level with legendary and unique game modes. Get your driver license and join the ultimate rally apocalypse.<br><br>UNIQUE GAME MODES<br> You will complete 32 license courses in total in order to became a real driver. Moreover you can join over 85 competitive races in Events mode for being the greatest rally racer of all time. Featuring Arena mode for drifting continues to build on the foundations set by the Rally Racer Drift game.<br><br>BREATH-TAKING RALLY CARS<br> You can join the races with the vehicle of your choice from 17 realistically made super cars. There will be upgrade and customization options waiting for you to express your style in many exciting races.<br><br>NEXT-GEN GRAPHIC AND SOUND TECHNOLOGY.<br> Rally Racer EVO® catches the next-gen graphic and sound technologies. Thanks to the graphic and sound options left for the player, you will experience the game without compromising from performance. <br><br> Key Features<br>*17 rally vehicles with customize and upgrade options.<br>*12 racing tracks with different atmospheric conditions.<br>*4 game modes; License, Events, Arena and Training.<br>* 85 competitive races in 6 racing events for Group B, 2WD, Crossover-SUV and Classic 4WD rally vehicles.(More to coming)<br>*32 courses for unique License mode.<br>*Realistic physics with consistent vehicle behaviors and easy to learn game-play.<br>*Highly optimized Next-Gen graphics and sounds.(Only 62MB)', '7023049.png', 'rally-racer-evo', '62M', 'Free', 'VO DIGITAL ARTS', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.vodigitalarts.rallyracerevo', NULL, '2', 4.00, '', 1, 1, 0, 22, 7, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2019-11-26 11:11:16', '2019-11-26 11:11:16'),
