nding.<br><br><br>CHALLENGE YOURSELF WITH MATH PUZZLES.<br><br>THE PUZZLES GET SLOWLY MORE CHALLENGING.<br><br>DEVELOP PROBLEM SOLVING AND LOGIC SKILLS.<br><br>TRAIN BOTH PARTS OF YOUR BRAIN.<br><br>YOUR FREE TIME IS MORE MEANINGFUL NOW.<br><br><br>Please don’t hesitate to reach to us for any kind of questions or comments via:<br>Instagram:	https://www.instagram.com/math.riddles/<br>E-mail:		blackgames.social@gmail.com', '8788793.png', 'math-riddles-and-puzzles-math-games', '20M', 'Free', 'Black Games', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.BlackGames.MathRiddles', NULL, '2', 4.00, '', 1, 1, 0, 22, 7, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2019-11-26 11:12:07', '2019-11-26 11:12:07'),
