(1119, 'Escape Alcatraz', 'No one has ever escaped and lived to tell. At least that\'s the official story...', NULL, 'Escape Alcatraz, the follow-up to Escape the Titanic delivers the next blockbuster adventure puzzler that puts you at the heart of an amazing true-life escape that remains unsolved to this day. Craft and assemble tools you’ll need, as you plan your high-stakes prison break. Can you devise an escape plan, fool the guards and find the right time to pull the trigger to freedom?<br><br>Never a dull moment as you pinch, twist, tap &amp; swipe your way through ingenious room-puzzle challenges.<br><br>With nothing to lose, do you have the smarts and tenacity to solve every puzzle and make it off The Rock!  ....Good luck!  <br><br>• 50+ clever puzzles - unlike anything you’ve ever seen.<br>• Integrated Hint System, if you need a little help.<br>• Find hidden tools to aid in your escape.<br>•  Hints and Answers available as IAP<br><br>Escape Alcatraz is a FREE-TO-TRY app. You can play the first chapter for free, if you want to unlock the epic FULL version, there is a one-time fee to purchase, plus a FREE option unlock the FULL version, too.', '1676006.png', 'escape-alcatraz', '65M', 'Free', 'App Holdings', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.freshgames.escapealcatraz', NULL, '2', 0.00, '', 0, 1, 0, 22, 7, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2019-12-17 19:29:55', '2019-12-17 19:29:55'),
