ed on tablets of all makes and sizes <br><br><br>*********************************<br>By downloading this game, you agree to the Terms of Service, Privacy Policy and the License Agreement. <br><br>*********************************', '1381215.png', 'underworld-empire', '58M', 'Free', 'Gaea Mobile Limited', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.kabam.underworldandroid', NULL, '2', 4.00, '', 1, 1, 0, 22, 7, 0, 0, 0, 0, '2019-12-23 19:25:07', '2019-12-23 19:25:07');
